title: [NDS] Olympic Battlefields - Terroristic Game for Nintendo DS
description:
Nintendo DS Terror Game - Olympic Battlefields 2008/2024

Do you desire to serve your interests while fighting terrorism? Why don't make an olympic discipline out of your annoyance?

Olympic Battlefields is the right game for you. Choose between the countries you would like to fight for. Israel, Palestina, China or Tibet!

Take your role as keeper of state control or as a radical terrorist.
